<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, July 1 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Saturday closed at 2427.36 points, down 1.08
points from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 8,060,175 shares changed hands in 1,508 deals and the
turnover stood at 36.74 billion rials (about 12.25 million U.S.
dollars).
</P>
<P>
The issues of 38 companies made gains while those of 24 others
declined. 
</P>
