the modernization of the exporting activity will be jointly
tackled with the private sector through the creation of working
groups.
</P>
<P>
Chile is negotiating at this time a political, economic, and
cooperation association with the European Union (EU), its
inclusion as a full member of Mercosur, and a free trade agreement
with South Korea.
</P>
<P>
Currently, Chile is an associate member of the Southern Common
Market, which includes Argentina, Brazil, Paraguay and Uruguay.
</P>
<P>
Argentina and Brazil, followed by the United States, Mexico
and the EU, are the countries that raise more barriers to their
commerce with Chile. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
